Phillip Reed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phillip_Reed 0 For similarly named individuals, see Phil Reid (disambiguation).Phillip Reed (March 25, 1908 – December 7, 1996) was an American actor. He was perhaps best known for his role as Steve Wilson in a series of four films (1947–1948) based on the Big Town radio series. For similarly_named_individuals , see Phil_Reid ( disambiguation ) .
